{"tid":1249890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有小小野想問，點寄份REO-1？ 我係網上登記，但想教人寄信","createTime":"2019-06-22T00:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T02:23:13.000Z","uid":69864,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d05c733d80fb4b6ed4257edddc23b47f00b86a33","tid":1249890,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"因為要整圖派街，唔想誤導人，所以請教下有寄reo－1既巴打經驗先。<br />\n<br />\n1. 份reo－1係唔係寄第一頁過去就ok？<br />\n2. 唔用佢第二頁個on9 design唔岩位既摺疊信封寄去得唔得,想用自己信封<br />\n3. 定其實係我on9 唔係佢個design on9，單純係我唔識摺（對唔到位)<br />\n4. 如果我用自己信封係唔係要連埋第二頁寄埋去？"},{"pid":"70e2f948ffcbd224c624206fc3eec90a6380379e","tid":1249890,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm0hK8z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm0hK8z.jpg&h=47303a98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c7472caf490632bdcdc23b16e9862432164aff","tid":1249890,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:47:16.000Z","msg":"第二張係唔洗寄..."},{"pid":"92355a79f70cae3785882d4f957ab14c27a4aa97","tid":1249890,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c7472caf490632bdcdc23b16e9862432164aff","tid":1249890,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:47:16.000Z","msg":"第二張係唔洗寄..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:51:03.000Z","msg":"所以只要PRINT 第一張比人填<br />\nReady一個寫好地址既信封,痴埋郵票比佢。<br />\n當時人係唔係就可以立即寄去申請?<br />\n<br />\n巴打我想係郵局附近派呢D野比人做登記,<br />\n可唔可以幫手諗諗除左我岩岩講呢3樣野仲有咩要準備?"},{"pid":"63a2a563d1d13d9579fbfa7592eff070e055b8e8","tid":1249890,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"印雙面啦 商業回郵 唔洗郵票"},{"pid":"6150a6c1843f74cbf776af64d8e3410a3efd69e9","tid":1249890,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63a2a563d1d13d9579fbfa7592eff070e055b8e8","tid":1249890,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"repl